There was one other sighting in Long Beach on or around October 6th 2013
Summary: One main object observed , than 2 more over 45 min.
divs: Sighting DetailsObserved bright gold object moving west in the morning sky as sun was rising. It stood out over southern california. Was not a plane or contrail. It was moving at a high altitude and speed. As i was pointing it out to my kids and pulling over we witnessed the 3rd object appear and seem to fall from the sky than the glowing contrail appeared. It looked like it was falling straight down and then it speed off to the west into the rising sun. It all lasted 4o minutes as we were driving back from the airport on the 405 freeway. I have pics of the 3rd object.
